Light microscopy (
<figureCitation box="[468,605,1223,1249]" captionStart="Figs 72–82" captionStartId="9.[189,241,1989,2015]" captionTargetBox="[189,1399,1693,1950]" captionTargetId="figure@9.[189,1399,1693,1950]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Figs 72–82. Luticola sp. Light micrographs of a population from Ile Saint-Paul. Scalebar: 10 μm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1133663/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Figs 72–82</figureCitation>
