<paragraph blockId="9.[189,1398,1551,1649]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
<heading fontSize="36" level="4" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" reason="4">
So far, this species has only been observed with light microscopy. Further studies and SEM observations will be necessary to determine its correct taxonomic position. The species was so far found in only two soil samples (A6 and A7) taken from Ile Saint-Paul. Both samples are dominated by 
